{"article_id":"PDAM85ZssHBIl1Ql","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Watch the CNN Republican debate Tuesday , December 15 at 6:00 p.m . ET and 8:30 p.m . ET .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The GOP establishment ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"confronted by a recalcitrant electorate","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that refuses to leave Donald Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"is being forced to take a fresh look at Ted Cruz , a man with grassroots strength in key early primary states and few friends in Washington .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Suddenly , the Republican Party 's best hope could be a man","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"hell-bent on transforming it :","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"a senator","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"who openly spars with fellow GOP colleagues ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"and has campaigned","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"by painting its leaders as spineless and feeble .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Headed into Tuesday 's CNN Republican presidential debate ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Cruz and Trump have turned Iowa into a two-man race ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"with the Texan leading in two new polls .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Cruz is up 31 % to Trump 's 21 % among likely GOP caucus-goers ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"according to the Bloomberg Politics-Des Moines Register poll","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"released Saturday .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"A Fox News poll Sunday has Cruz leading Trump 28 % to 26 % .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"A small and growing number of Republicans","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"allied with the establishment","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"-- the force","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"long thought to quickly consolidate against a surging Cruz bid --","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"are coming to terms with the idea","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that he may be palatable in an election cycle","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"where Trump has pushed the envelope well beyond what they considered acceptable .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"`` Oh God , yes , ''","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"said Ed Rogers , a top Republican lobbyist ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"when asked if he 'd prefer Cruz .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"`` Compared to Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he 's OK . ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Establishment Republicans had enough of a problem","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"when Trump began his populist-fueled move to the top of national polls ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"where he has stubbornly remained for five months .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"But Cruz 's steady rise means","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"even if Trump were taken out by a well-financed negative campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"they might have to deal with a stronger Cruz ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"who has more political polish than the more improvisational Trump .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"`` If you talk to my peers around town ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"collectively it 's an appreciation the guy is smart as hell , ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"explained a senior Washington Republican","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"who is backing another candidate .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` He can be a more acceptable alternative to Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"if it comes to that . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"The irony has n't escaped them .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Said the Republican :","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"`` It 's an interesting life","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"-- and everything 's relative . ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Most establishment Republicans have been drawn to the half-dozen candidates","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who come from that wing of the party ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"especially Florida Sen. Marco Rubio ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who has lived in the mid-teens in most polls ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"who has dropped down to 3 % nationally .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"given Cruz 's surging poll numbers and Trump 's remarkable political durability ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"some wonder","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"if it could be Cruz","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that emerges as the compromise candidate .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` The second he starts to look like a winner in Washington , ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Rogers said ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` he 's going to have a bunch of new friends . ''","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"It 's a dilemma","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"swatted away on Capitol Hill","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"-- perhaps optimistically .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Asked about choosing Trump or Cruz ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"2008 nominee Sen. John McCain would only allow","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that they are `` smart people . ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Bush backer Sen. Susan Collins would just offer","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"that they are `` obviously not my choice . ''","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"And there 's no guarantee","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"either one can beat Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"`` He 's not as outrageous as Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"but I do n't know","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that he 's any more electable than Trump , ''","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"said Charlie Black , a senior adviser to Republican presidential campaigns for over two decades .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Brian Walsh , a longtime Senate campaign aide , said","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"it 's an out-of-control Trump","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"-- not an in-control Cruz --","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that explains the Texan 's growing appeal .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` Trump has gone so far","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that it has in some ways masked how problematic Cruz would be as the nominee as well , ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Despite his background as an Ivy League-educated attorney and his time in the Bush administration ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Cruz rose to prominence as a tea party darling","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"who became the national face of the 2013 government shutdown .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Cruz has spent the two years since working","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"to salvage his relationship with some potential investors in his campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but he has reveled in his image as a Washington bad boy , the only senator","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"willing to do on Capitol Hill what he campaigned on back at home .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"It 's something","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"that has made him enemies in Washington ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"where he has not convinced a single Senate colleague to back his campaign .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Cruz helped push Republicans to shut down the government in a high-stakes fight over Obamacare , a strategy","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that failed to get results","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but did n't cause a predicted electoral meltdown .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"On the trail , he has shown no willingness","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to moderate his positions ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"bragging about his conservative purity and his rabble-rousing reputation in the Capitol .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"even compared to Cruz 's burn-it-down rhetoric ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Trump 's campaign has been more incendiary and worrisome for party elders","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"determined to beat likely Democratic nominee Hillary Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"The mogul had harsh things to say about Hispanics , prisoners of war , women in the media , the disabled , and most recently , Muslims ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"who","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"he thinks","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"temporarily should not be allowed to enter the United States .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"And most concerning for GOP leaders ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Trump has frequently floated leaving the Republican Party altogether","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"to mount an independent bid ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"which would significantly increase Clinton 's chances","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"of winning the White House .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"The pair appears to be heading toward a clash","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that Cruz , at least , long sought to delay .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"On Friday evening ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"about 24 hours after audio leaked","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"of Cruz","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"questioning Trump 's judgment at a private fundraiser ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"the real estate mogul launched his first attacks on Cruz .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Cruz had attempted to head that off","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"by alleging","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"that mainstream Republicans were trying to sow discord .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"`` The Establishment 's only hope :","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"Trump & me in a cage match , ''","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"he tweeted Friday morning .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"`` Sorry to disappoint -","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"@ realdonaldtrump is terrific .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"# DealWithIt ''","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Cruz has done little","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"to woo the Republicans","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"he used as his bogeyman :","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"He has raised the lion 's share of his money far from the New York-to-Washington corridor ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"raced to the party 's right flank on every issue of the day ,","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"and campaigned loudly on the polarizing social issues","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"one well-placed Republican said","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"puts some contributors permanently out of reach .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Cruz , on paper , should not be as repellent to the GOP political class","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"as he is .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Nurtured by the George W. Bush network in Texas ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"he served as solicitor general","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"before winning an upset bid in the 2012 Republican U.S. Senate primary .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"To Stuart Stevens , the chief strategist for Mitt Romney 's 2012 campaign , that resume should theoretically make him attractive to the party 's elite .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"`` At a core of Cruz 's candidacy is a great phonyism , ''","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Stevens said of the self-stylized insurgent .","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"`` You can wear all the plaid shirts","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"and shoot off all the automatic weapons","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"you want ,","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"but you 're an insider . ''","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"And some of his positions , such as on national security , do hew closely to the party 's center .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"As Cruz held court on MSNBC 's `` Morning Joe '' last week ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"`` you could 've sworn","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"he was working for George Herbert Walker Bush on his foreign policy , ''","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"a senior Republican said .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"But a leading Republican in frequent touch with high-level donors , said","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"even though those contributors may despise Cruz ,","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"they are learning to live with him .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"`` If that 's what we need to do","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"to beat Trump , ''","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"the Republican said ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"`` then that 's what you get . ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":321,"left":0,"right":320,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":320,"left":170,"right":319,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":164,"right":169,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":1,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":165,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":7,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":8,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":319,"left":188,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":176,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":172,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":11,"right":171,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":171,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":174,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":14,"right":173,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":182,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":179,"right":181,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":18,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":19,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":22,"right":180,"relation":"elabora